Maurice Costello https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maurice_Costello 0 Maurice George Costello (February 22, 1877 – October 29, 1950) was a prominent American vaudeville actor of the late 1890s and early 1900s, who later played a principal role in early American films, as leading man, supporting player and director.
